Package de.oth.blocklib.graphRenderer

This package contains all necessary classes for rendering a given graph to visualize the results of pathfinding or graph creation
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GraphMarker
    Any type of marker which is used to visualize a node in a graph should use this interface
    GraphRenderer
    The interface for any type of class which is used to display a graph.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnimatedBlockGraphRenderer
    Visualizes a Graph or a Path by marking the block on the ground and animates the direction.
    AnimatedEntityGraphRenderer
    Animates the EntityGraphRendere by showing the direction of the Path.
    BlockGraphMarker
    This Marker is the visualization of a position by a block on the ground.
    BlockGraphRenderer
    Visualizes a Graph or a Path by setting red blocks on the ground. !!
    EntityEdgesGraphRenderer
    Visualizes a Graph by setting entities at the location of its nodes as well es Entities at the location of the edges.
    EntityGraphMarker
    This Marker is the visualization of a position in a graph.
    EntityGraphRenderer
    Visualizes the nodes of a graph with Entities.
